#message:10:021
{
	[Style Right]
	Yoshi![Pause 10] I mean, welcome to[BR]
	Yoshi's Village.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I am the Chieftain here.[BR]
	[Pause 10]I was born and raised on[BR]
	Yo'ster Isle, but I have since[BR]
	moved to this locale.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	The Yoshis here have recently[BR]
	lost their previous chieftain a[BR]
	decade ago, so I was happy to[BR]
	take over in his stead.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Now look at me, I'm guarding[BR]
	and leading a brand new [BR]
	generation![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Not to mention, these fine[BR]
	Yoshis have even gone on to[BR]
	have kids of their own.[BR]
	[Pause 10]I feel like a grandfather,[Wave] haha![/fx][BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Anyways, do stay a while.[BR]
	[Pause 10]We carry melons and treats made[BR]
	from the local coconuts.[BR]
	[Pause 10]A delicacy you'll enjoy, for sure.[Wait][End]
}

