#message:10:0A8
{
	[Style Right]
	Ah, another day, another time[BR]
	to greet mankind.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	The jungle sure is a wonderful[BR]
	place for nature to flourish.[BR]
	[Pause 10]I can feel my synergy resonate[BR]
	with the bountiful red.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	What's the matter?[BR]
	[Pause 10]Never seen a red jungle[BR]
	before, human?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[Wave]Oh ho ho ho![/fx][BR]
	[Pause 5]I don't blame you.[BR]
	[Pause 5]Mankind has time to adjust to[BR]
	all sorts of things.[BR]
	[Wait][next]
	The bounds of this jungle are[BR]
	thankfully quite safe from the[BR]
	transgressions of electronics.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Say... [Pause 10]You wouldn't happen to[BR]
	know my other Bub-Ulb friends[BR]
	would you?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	We were all planning to rally[BR]
	and return to our home in[BR]
	[SaveColor][Color:1E]Flower Land[RestoreColor],[Pause 10] however we left[BR]
	in fear of our lives.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Back home, an awful yokai has[BR]
	been terrorizing the gardens.[BR]
	[Pause 30]Do not worry, you will know the[BR]
	full tale soon enough.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Your current target is to[BR]
	scour this jungle in the hopes[BR]
	that you'll bring value to your[BR]
	life, human.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Mankind's afraid to step back[BR]
	and appreciate what life brought[BR]
	them before the rise of tech and[BR]
	supercomputers.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[PrintGrowing]You have time.[/fx][BR]
	[Pause 10]Savour this jungle while you[BR]
	still can.[Wait][End]
}

